com.azure.storage.blob.batch

Class BlobBatchClientBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.azure.storage.blob.batch.BlobBatchClientBuilder

  • public final class BlobBatchClientBuilder
extends Object
    This class provides a fluent builder API to help aid the configuration and instantiation of BlobBatchClients and BlobBatchAsyncClients when buildClient and buildAsyncClient as called respectively.

      • serviceVersion

        public BlobBatchClientBuilder serviceVersion(BlobServiceVersion version)
        Sets the BlobServiceVersion that is used when making API requests.

        If a service version is not provided, the service version that will be used will be the latest known service version based on the version of the client library being used. If no service version is specified, updating to a newer version the client library will have the result of potentially moving to a newer service version.

        Parameters:
        version - BlobServiceVersion of the service to be used when making requests.
        Returns:
        the updated BlobClientBuilder object
